                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Dawson</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Petropolis</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1902-07-31">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 31, 1902</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Dawson reports that vigorous steps have been taken in the Thomsen
                    inheritance tax case by Minister Bryan.)</p>
            </div>
